	<TextInfo>
		<Text Type="Business Summary" lastModified="2015-08-25T09:33:05">Datatec Limited is an information and communication technology (ICT) solutions and services company. The Company offers its services in the technology, integration and consulting sectors of the ICT market. The Company's segments include Westcon, Logicalis, Consulting Services and Corporate. The Westcon segment is engaged in the distribution of networking, security, and unified communications products and data center solutions. The Logicalis segment is engaged in providing ICT infrastructure solutions and services. The Consulting Services segment offers strategic and technical consulting. The Corporate segment includes head office companies, including Datatec Financial Services, a capital/leasing business under development and Company consolidation adjustments. The Company operates in around 60 countries across North America, Latin America, Europe, Africa, the Middle East and Asia-Pacific.</Text>
		<Text Type="Financial Summary" lastModified="2016-02-01T23:58:12">BRIEF: For the six months ended 31 August 2015, Datatec Ltd. revenues increased 10% to $3.29B. Net income decreased 23% to $24.4M. Revenues reflect Westcon segment increase of 12% to $2.51B, Logicalis segment increase of 5% to $751.4M. Net income was offset by Logicalis segment income decrease of 20% to $24.3M, Westcon segment income decrease of 8% to $39.5M, Consulting Services segment loss totaling $881K vs. income of $956K.</Text>
	</TextInfo>
